<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to StreamAPI Newsletter</title>
    <style>
        /* Email-specific styles */
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #f8f9fa;
            background-color: #1a202c;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .email-header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            background-color: #2d3748;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .email-logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #10b981;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .email-body {
            background-color: #374151;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .email-footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #9ca3af;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #10b981;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        h1, h2, h3 {
            color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .social-links {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .social-links a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 0 10px;
            color: #9ca3af;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        hr {
            border: 0;
            height: 1px;
            background: #4b5563;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .content-section {
            background-color: #2d3748;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .movie-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .movie-item {
            text-align: center;
        }
        .movie-item img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .movie-title {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #e2e8f0;
            white-space: nowrap;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="email-header">
            <div class="email-logo">
                <span style="color: #10b981;">&#9658;</span> StreamAPI
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="email-body">
            <h1>Welcome to StreamAPI Newsletter!</h1>
            
            <p>Hello there,</p>
            
            <p>Thank you for subscribing to the StreamAPI newsletter! You'll now receive the latest updates on movies, TV shows, and other exciting content delivered straight to your inbox.</p>
            
            <div class="content-section">
                <h3><span style="color: #10b981;">&#9733;</span> What to expect from our newsletter:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Weekly updates on new movie and TV show releases</li>
                    <li>Personalized recommendations based on popular trends</li>
                    <li>Exclusive insights and behind-the-scenes content</li>
                    <li>Special announcements and platform updates</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="content-section">
                <h3><span style="color: #10b981;">&#9733;</span> Trending This Week</h3>
                <div class="movie-grid">
                    <% if (locals.trendingMovies && trendingMovies.length > 0) { %>
                        <% trendingMovies.forEach(movie => { %>
                            <div class="movie-item">
                                <% if (movie.poster) { %>
                                    <img src="<%= movie.poster %>" alt="<%= movie.title %>" style="width: 150px; height: 225px; object-fit: cover;">
                                <% } else { %>
                                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150x225/2d3748/10b981?text=No+Image" alt="<%= movie.title %>" style="width: 150px; height: 225px;">
                                <% } %>
                                <div class="movie-title"><%= movie.title %></div>
                            </div>
                        <% }); %>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <div class="movie-item">
                            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150x225/2d3748/10b981?text=Movie+1" alt="Movie">
                            <div class="movie-title">Action Movie Title</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="movie-item">
                            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150x225/2d3748/10b981?text=Movie+2" alt="Movie">
                            <div class="movie-title">Comedy Film Title</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="movie-item">
                            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150x225/2d3748/10b981?text=Movie+3" alt="Movie">
                            <div class="movie-title">Drama Movie Title</div>
                        </div>
                    <% } %>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="<%= siteUrl %>" class="button">Visit StreamAPI</a>
            </div>
            
            <hr>
            
            <p>We're excited to have you as part of our community!</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>The StreamAPI Team</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="email-footer">
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="#">Github</a> &bull;
                <a href="#">Twitter</a> &bull;
                <a href="#">Discord</a> &bull;
                <a href="#">Instagram</a>
            </div>
            
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> StreamAPI. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>Created by <a href="https://github.com/BotCoder254" style="color: #10b981;">@BotCoder254</a></p>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 11px;">
                This email was sent to <%= email %>. If you didn't subscribe to our newsletter, you can safely ignore this email or <a href="<%= siteUrl %>/unsubscribe?email=<%= email %>" style="color: #10b981;">unsubscribe here</a>.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 